{"tid":1597480,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"再一次證明 同林鄭對話係無用的！","createTime":"2019-09-27T03:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T05:15:32.000Z","uid":199050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc917a4a4b96d58eef7e0675da6620f5a7edb58","tid":1597480,"uid":199050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地要好好利用呢個機會反擊！</span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭話我地暴力，叫我地用對話解決，整咗個對話大會出嚟<br />\n<br />\n好！我地俾多次機會佢，坐低去傾。三個月後，我地又嘗試重複五大訴求。但大家都睇到佢嘅回應就係不回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係我地再嘗試用和平方法表達，但佢都唔理。除咗暴力升級，仲有咩方法可以做？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地一定要杯葛呢個對話會！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要俾全世界睇到呢個只係佢嘅公關show！毫無誠意可言！<br />\n<br />\n我地係多番嘗試用和平方法表達，但係無用！<br />\n<br />\n為咗保護自己，守護香港最後一道防線，逼於無奈先會將武力升級！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港  時代革命<br />\n五大訴求  缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"fe57e19f9b5b33a6872ff711f40ba0794814e9c2","tid":1597480,"uid":199050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"3243d29795902f4bac122f9211a3db18ae32a7c7","tid":1597480,"uid":199050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:02:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"978b323d059aad98c96c29249a214fd14e69b23f","tid":1597480,"uid":199050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:02:26.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"524a95b19b2aaa990716a8eace7e370c15088071","tid":1597480,"uid":260645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4eed102d6f81cc43cf801dfff8c50dff13ce6e","tid":1597480,"uid":199050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"524a95b19b2aaa990716a8eace7e370c15088071","tid":1597480,"uid":260645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:06:38.000Z",